<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nnthr bạsmk kl ạ̉rwạḥ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- nnthr bạsmk kl ạ̉rwạḥ .. ạ̉rwạḥ ạlsẖr wkl jrạḥ
 nʿln ḥmạytnạ yạ yswʿ fyk .. rwḥk ybhjnạ bạlạ̉frạḥ
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉frạḥ msẖ mmkn ynzʿhạ .. ʿdw ạlkẖyr wạnt zạrʿhạ
 wạlbhjẗ wạlfrḥẗ wạhbhạ .. bdmk rby yạ ṣạnʿhạ
 2- mạʿrfsẖ ạ̉ḥzạn wạnt mʿạyạ .. mjdaⁿạ lyk wḥdk yạ hnạyạ
 ḥmlt ḥmwly wkẖṭạyạyạ .. wạ̉ʿṭytny ạlnṣrẗ yạ rjạyạ
 3- ạ̉nạ knt bạsʿy̱ wrạ srạb .. kạn qlby mtʿlq btrạb
 ạ̉sẖbʿt ḥyạty bʿd ʿdẖạb .. wqryb htạkẖdny mʿ ạlạ̉ḥbạb</lyrics>
